                        <li xml:id="auto_l8juik2s"><p xml:id="auto_7nr5gdgb">A cylindrical storage container has radius 0.4 m and height 1.2 m. Calculate its volume in litres. (Use <m>\pi \approx 3.14</m>.)</p></li>
                        <li xml:id="auto_8y3oi3v9"><p xml:id="auto_by1cj662">Explain why knowing how to calculate volume is important in everyday life. Give two examples.</p></li>
                    </ol>
